# Rock Paper Scissors Game 🎮

A simple Rock Paper Scissors game built using Python.

## Description

This is a command-line game where the user plays Rock, Paper, Scissors against the computer. The computer randomly chooses an option, and the winner is decided based on the game rules.

## Features

- User vs Computer gameplay
- Random computer choices
- Rock, Paper, and Scissors ASCII art
- Win, Lose, and Draw conditions
- Input validation for user choices

## Technologies Used

- Python 3
- Random Module


## What I Learned

- Conditional Statements (if-elif-else)
- Random Number Generation
- User Input Handling
- Game Logic Implementation
- ASCII Art in Python

